    FROM [ProductImages] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] IN (

SELECT [p].[Id], COALESCE([p].[Name], N'') AS [Name], COALESCE([p].[Code], N'') AS [Code], COALESCE([p].[Description], N'') AS [Description], [p].[Price], [p].[StockQuantity], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[IsDisplay]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
WHERE [p].[IsDelete] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [p].[IsDelete] IS NULL
ORDER BY [p].[CreatedDate] DESC
OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
2024-07-01 00:10:21.065 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[@__productIds_0='?' (Size = 4000)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedBy], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[CreatedID], [t0].[DeleteBy], [t0].[DeleteId], [t0].[DeleteTime], [t0].[ImageFeature], [t0].[IsDelete], [t0].[IsThumbnail], [t0].[Path], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[UpdatedBy], [t0].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[UpdatedID]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[ProductId]
    FROM [ProductImages] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] IN (
        SELECT [p0].[value]
        FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p0]
    ) AND [p].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    GROUP BY [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedBy], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[CreatedID], [t1].[DeleteBy], [t1].[DeleteId], [t1].[DeleteTime], [t1].[ImageFeature], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[IsThumbnail], [t1].[Path], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[UpdatedBy], [t1].[UpdatedDate], [t1].[UpdatedID]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreatedBy], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[CreatedID], [p1].[DeleteBy], [p1].[DeleteId], [p1].[DeleteTime], [p1].[ImageFeature], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[IsThumbnail], [p1].[Path], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[UpdatedBy], [p1].[UpdatedDate], [p1].[UpdatedID], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [p1].[ProductId] ORDER BY [p1].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [ProductImages] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ProductId] IN (
            SELECT [p2].[value]
            FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p2]
        ) AND [p1].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[ProductId] = [t0].[ProductId]

FROM [Products] AS [p]

2024-07-01 00:17:21.467 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[@__productIds_0='?' (Size = 4000)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedBy], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[CreatedID], [t0].[DeleteBy], [t0].[DeleteId], [t0].[DeleteTime], [t0].[ImageFeature], [t0].[IsDelete], [t0].[IsThumbnail], [t0].[Path], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[UpdatedBy], [t0].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[UpdatedID]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[ProductId]
    FROM [ProductImages] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] IN (
        SELECT [p0].[value]
        FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p0]
    ) AND [p].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    GROUP BY [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedBy], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[CreatedID], [t1].[DeleteBy], [t1].[DeleteId], [t1].[DeleteTime], [t1].[ImageFeature], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[IsThumbnail], [t1].[Path], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[UpdatedBy], [t1].[UpdatedDate], [t1].[UpdatedID]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreatedBy], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[CreatedID], [p1].[DeleteBy], [p1].[DeleteId], [p1].[DeleteTime], [p1].[ImageFeature], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[IsThumbnail], [p1].[Path], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[UpdatedBy], [p1].[UpdatedDate], [p1].[UpdatedID], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [p1].[ProductId] ORDER BY [p1].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [ProductImages] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ProductId] IN (
            SELECT [p2].[value]
            FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p2]
        ) AND [p1].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[ProductId] = [t0].[ProductId]

    FROM [ProductImages] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] IN (
        SELECT [p0].[value]
        FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p0]

) AS [t]

    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedBy], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[CreatedID], [t1].[DeleteBy], [t1].[DeleteId], [t1].[DeleteTime], [t1].[ImageFeature], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[IsThumbnail], [t1].[Path], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[UpdatedBy], [t1].[UpdatedDate], [t1].[UpdatedID]

        ) AND [p1].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)

SELECT [p1].[CategoryId], COALESCE(SUM([o].[TotalAmount]), 0.0E0) AS [Revenue]
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [OrderItems] AS [o0] ON [o].[Id] = [o0].[OrderId]
INNER JOIN [ProductVariants] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductVariantId] = [p].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p1] ON [p0].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
WHERE ([o].[IsDelete] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsDelete] IS NULL) AND ([o].[IsCancelled] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsCancelled] IS NULL) AND ([p1].[CategoryId] = @__get_Item_0 OR [p1].[CategoryId] = @__get_Item_1)
GROUP BY [p1].[CategoryId]

        SELECT [p0].[value]

SELECT [t].[Key] AS [Label_Day], COALESCE(SUM([t].[TotalAmount]), 0.0E0) AS [Revenue], COUNT(*) AS [CountOrder]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[TotalAmount], CONVERT(date, [o].[CreatedDate]) AS [Key]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE ([o].[IsDelete] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsDelete] IS NULL) AND ([o].[IsCancelled] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsCancelled] IS NULL)
) AS [t]
GROUP BY [t].[Key]

    FROM [ProductImages] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] IN (

        ) AND [p1].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)

SELECT [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedBy], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[CreatedID], [t0].[DeleteBy], [t0].[DeleteId], [t0].[DeleteTime], [t0].[ImageFeature], [t0].[IsDelete], [t0].[IsThumbnail], [t0].[Path], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[UpdatedBy], [t0].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[UpdatedID]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[ProductId]
    FROM [ProductImages] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] IN (
        SELECT [p0].[value]
        FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p0]
    ) AND [p].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    GROUP BY [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedBy], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[CreatedID], [t1].[DeleteBy], [t1].[DeleteId], [t1].[DeleteTime], [t1].[ImageFeature], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[IsThumbnail], [t1].[Path], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[UpdatedBy], [t1].[UpdatedDate], [t1].[UpdatedID]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreatedBy], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[CreatedID], [p1].[DeleteBy], [p1].[DeleteId], [p1].[DeleteTime], [p1].[ImageFeature], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[IsThumbnail], [p1].[Path], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[UpdatedBy], [p1].[UpdatedDate], [p1].[UpdatedID], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [p1].[ProductId] ORDER BY [p1].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [ProductImages] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ProductId] IN (
            SELECT [p2].[value]
            FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p2]
        ) AND [p1].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[ProductId] = [t0].[ProductId]

SELECT [t].[Key] AS [Label_Day], COALESCE(SUM([t].[TotalAmount]), 0.0E0) AS [Revenue], COUNT(*) AS [CountOrder]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[TotalAmount], CONVERT(date, [o].[CreatedDate]) AS [Key]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE ([o].[IsDelete] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsDelete] IS NULL) AND ([o].[IsCancelled] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsCancelled] IS NULL)
) AS [t]
GROUP BY [t].[Key]

    SELECT TOP(1) [o2].[Price]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o1]
    INNER JOIN [OrderItems] AS [o2] ON [o1].[Id] = [o2].[OrderId]
    INNER JOIN [ProductVariants] AS [p1] ON [o2].[ProductVariantId] = [p1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p2] ON [p1].[ProductId] = [p2].[Id]

    FROM [ProductImages] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] IN (
        SELECT [p0].[value]
        FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p0]

) AS [t]

    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedBy], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[CreatedID], [t1].[DeleteBy], [t1].[DeleteId], [t1].[DeleteTime], [t1].[ImageFeature], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[IsThumbnail], [t1].[Path], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[UpdatedBy], [t1].[UpdatedDate], [t1].[UpdatedID]

            FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p2]
        ) AND [p1].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t1]

    FROM [ProductImages] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] IN (
        SELECT [p0].[value]
        FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p0]
    ) AND [p].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    GROUP BY [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedBy], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[CreatedID], [t1].[DeleteBy], [t1].[DeleteId], [t1].[DeleteTime], [t1].[ImageFeature], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[IsThumbnail], [t1].[Path], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[UpdatedBy], [t1].[UpdatedDate], [t1].[UpdatedID]

        FROM [ProductImages] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ProductId] IN (
            SELECT [p2].[value]
            FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p2]
        ) AND [p1].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t1]

SELECT [t].[Key] AS [Label_Day], COALESCE(SUM([t].[TotalAmount]), 0.0E0) AS [Revenue], COUNT(*) AS [CountOrder]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[TotalAmount], CONVERT(date, [o].[CreatedDate]) AS [Key]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE ([o].[IsDelete] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsDelete] IS NULL) AND ([o].[IsCancelled] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsCancelled] IS NULL)
) AS [t]
GROUP BY [t].[Key]

    SELECT TOP(1) [o2].[Price]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o1]
    INNER JOIN [OrderItems] AS [o2] ON [o1].[Id] = [o2].[OrderId]
    INNER JOIN [ProductVariants] AS [p1] ON [o2].[ProductVariantId] = [p1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p2] ON [p1].[ProductId] = [p2].[Id]

SELECT [p1].[CategoryId], COALESCE(SUM([o].[TotalAmount]), 0.0E0) AS [Revenue]
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [OrderItems] AS [o0] ON [o].[Id] = [o0].[OrderId]
INNER JOIN [ProductVariants] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductVariantId] = [p].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p1] ON [p0].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
WHERE ([o].[IsDelete] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsDelete] IS NULL) AND ([o].[IsCancelled] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsCancelled] IS NULL) AND ([p1].[CategoryId] = @__get_Item_0 OR [p1].[CategoryId] = @__get_Item_1)
GROUP BY [p1].[CategoryId]

SELECT [t].[Key] AS [Label_Day], COALESCE(SUM([t].[TotalAmount]), 0.0E0) AS [Revenue], COUNT(*) AS [CountOrder]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[TotalAmount], CONVERT(date, [o].[CreatedDate]) AS [Key]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE ([o].[IsDelete] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsDelete] IS NULL) AND ([o].[IsCancelled] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsCancelled] IS NULL)
) AS [t]

        SELECT [p0].[value]

    ) AND [p].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)

) AS [t]

        FROM [ProductImages] AS [p1]

    ) AS [t1]

2024-07-01 00:39:55.759 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (6ms) [Parameters=[@__p_2='?' (DbType = Int32), @__startDate_Date_0='?' (DbType = DateTime2), @__endDate_Date_1='?' (DbType = DateTime2)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT TOP(@__p_2) [p0].[Id] AS [ProductId], [p0].[Name] AS [ProductName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [o2].[Price]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o1]
    INNER JOIN [OrderItems] AS [o2] ON [o1].[Id] = [o2].[OrderId]
    INNER JOIN [ProductVariants] AS [p1] ON [o2].[ProductVariantId] = [p1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p2] ON [p1].[ProductId] = [p2].[Id]
    WHERE CONVERT(date, [o1].[CreatedDate]) >= @__startDate_Date_0 AND CONVERT(date, [o1].[CreatedDate]) <= @__endDate_Date_1 AND ([o1].[IsDelete] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o1].[IsDelete] IS NULL) AND ([o1].[IsCancelled] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o1].[IsCancelled] IS NULL) AND [p0].[Id] = [p2].[Id] AND [p0].[Code] = [p2].[Code] AND ([p0].[CreatedBy] = [p2].[CreatedBy] OR ([p0].[CreatedBy] IS NULL AND [p2].[CreatedBy] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[CreatedDate] = [p2].[CreatedDate] OR ([p0].[CreatedDate] IS NULL AND [p2].[CreatedDate] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[CreatedID] = [p2].[CreatedID] OR ([p0].[CreatedID] IS NULL AND [p2].[CreatedID] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[DeleteBy] = [p2].[DeleteBy] OR ([p0].[DeleteBy] IS NULL AND [p2].[DeleteBy] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[DeleteId] = [p2].[DeleteId] OR ([p0].[DeleteId] IS NULL AND [p2].[DeleteId] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[DeleteTime] = [p2].[DeleteTime] OR ([p0].[DeleteTime] IS NULL AND [p2].[DeleteTime] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[Description] = [p2].[Description] OR ([p0].[Description] IS NULL AND [p2].[Description] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[IsDelete] = [p2].[IsDelete] OR ([p0].[IsDelete] IS NULL AND [p2].[IsDelete] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[IsDisplay] = [p2].[IsDisplay] OR ([p0].[IsDisplay] IS NULL AND [p2].[IsDisplay] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[Name] = [p2].[Name] OR ([p0].[Name] IS NULL AND [p2].[Name] IS NULL)) AND [p0].[Price] = [p2].[Price] AND ([p0].[StockQuantity] = [p2].[StockQuantity] OR ([p0].[StockQuantity] IS NULL AND [p2].[StockQuantity] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[UpdatedBy] = [p2].[UpdatedBy] OR ([p0].[UpdatedBy] IS NULL AND [p2].[UpdatedBy] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[UpdatedDate] = [p2].[UpdatedDate] OR ([p0].[UpdatedDate] IS NULL AND [p2].[UpdatedDate] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[UpdatedID] = [p2].[UpdatedID] OR ([p0].[UpdatedID] IS NULL AND [p2].[UpdatedID] IS NULL))), 0.0E0) AS [ProductPrice], COALESCE(SUM([o0].[Quantity]), 0) AS [TotalQuantitySold]
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [OrderItems] AS [o0] ON [o].[Id] = [o0].[OrderId]
INNER JOIN [ProductVariants] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductVariantId] = [p].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]

ORDER BY COALESCE(SUM([o0].[Quantity]), 0) DESC

FROM [Orders] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [OrderItems] AS [o0] ON [o].[Id] = [o0].[OrderId]
INNER JOIN [ProductVariants] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductVariantId] = [p].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p1] ON [p0].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
WHERE ([o].[IsDelete] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsDelete] IS NULL) AND ([o].[IsCancelled] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsCancelled] IS NULL) AND ([p1].[CategoryId] = @__get_Item_0 OR [p1].[CategoryId] = @__get_Item_1)

2024-07-01 00:41:49.791 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Key] AS [Label_Day], COALESCE(SUM([t].[TotalAmount]), 0.0E0) AS [Revenue], COUNT(*) AS [CountOrder]
FROM (
    SELECT [o].[TotalAmount], CONVERT(date, [o].[CreatedDate]) AS [Key]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE ([o].[IsDelete] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsDelete] IS NULL) AND ([o].[IsCancelled] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o].[IsCancelled] IS NULL)
) AS [t]
GROUP BY [t].[Key]

    ) AND [p].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    GROUP BY [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedBy], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[CreatedID], [t1].[DeleteBy], [t1].[DeleteId], [t1].[DeleteTime], [t1].[ImageFeature], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[IsThumbnail], [t1].[Path], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[UpdatedBy], [t1].[UpdatedDate], [t1].[UpdatedID]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreatedBy], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[CreatedID], [p1].[DeleteBy], [p1].[DeleteId], [p1].[DeleteTime], [p1].[ImageFeature], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[IsThumbnail], [p1].[Path], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[UpdatedBy], [p1].[UpdatedDate], [p1].[UpdatedID], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [p1].[ProductId] ORDER BY [p1].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [ProductImages] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ProductId] IN (
            SELECT [p2].[value]
            FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p2]
        ) AND [p1].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[ProductId] = [t0].[ProductId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[ProductId]
    FROM [ProductImages] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] IN (
        SELECT [p0].[value]
        FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p0]
    ) AND [p].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    GROUP BY [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t]

        FROM [ProductImages] AS [p1]

        ) AND [p1].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t1]

FROM (
    SELECT [o].[TotalAmount], CONVERT(date, [o].[CreatedDate]) AS [Key]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]

) AS [t]
GROUP BY [t].[Key]

2024-07-01 00:49:01.681 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (15ms) [Parameters=[@__p_2='?' (DbType = Int32), @__startDate_Date_0='?' (DbType = DateTime2), @__endDate_Date_1='?' (DbType = DateTime2)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT TOP(@__p_2) [p0].[Id] AS [ProductId], [p0].[Name] AS [ProductName], COALESCE((
    SELECT TOP(1) [o2].[Price]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o1]
    INNER JOIN [OrderItems] AS [o2] ON [o1].[Id] = [o2].[OrderId]
    INNER JOIN [ProductVariants] AS [p1] ON [o2].[ProductVariantId] = [p1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p2] ON [p1].[ProductId] = [p2].[Id]
    WHERE CONVERT(date, [o1].[CreatedDate]) >= @__startDate_Date_0 AND CONVERT(date, [o1].[CreatedDate]) <= @__endDate_Date_1 AND ([o1].[IsDelete] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o1].[IsDelete] IS NULL) AND ([o1].[IsCancelled] <> CAST(1 AS bit) OR [o1].[IsCancelled] IS NULL) AND [p0].[Id] = [p2].[Id] AND [p0].[Code] = [p2].[Code] AND ([p0].[CreatedBy] = [p2].[CreatedBy] OR ([p0].[CreatedBy] IS NULL AND [p2].[CreatedBy] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[CreatedDate] = [p2].[CreatedDate] OR ([p0].[CreatedDate] IS NULL AND [p2].[CreatedDate] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[CreatedID] = [p2].[CreatedID] OR ([p0].[CreatedID] IS NULL AND [p2].[CreatedID] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[DeleteBy] = [p2].[DeleteBy] OR ([p0].[DeleteBy] IS NULL AND [p2].[DeleteBy] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[DeleteId] = [p2].[DeleteId] OR ([p0].[DeleteId] IS NULL AND [p2].[DeleteId] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[DeleteTime] = [p2].[DeleteTime] OR ([p0].[DeleteTime] IS NULL AND [p2].[DeleteTime] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[Description] = [p2].[Description] OR ([p0].[Description] IS NULL AND [p2].[Description] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[IsDelete] = [p2].[IsDelete] OR ([p0].[IsDelete] IS NULL AND [p2].[IsDelete] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[IsDisplay] = [p2].[IsDisplay] OR ([p0].[IsDisplay] IS NULL AND [p2].[IsDisplay] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[Name] = [p2].[Name] OR ([p0].[Name] IS NULL AND [p2].[Name] IS NULL)) AND [p0].[Price] = [p2].[Price] AND ([p0].[StockQuantity] = [p2].[StockQuantity] OR ([p0].[StockQuantity] IS NULL AND [p2].[StockQuantity] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[UpdatedBy] = [p2].[UpdatedBy] OR ([p0].[UpdatedBy] IS NULL AND [p2].[UpdatedBy] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[UpdatedDate] = [p2].[UpdatedDate] OR ([p0].[UpdatedDate] IS NULL AND [p2].[UpdatedDate] IS NULL)) AND ([p0].[UpdatedID] = [p2].[UpdatedID] OR ([p0].[UpdatedID] IS NULL AND [p2].[UpdatedID] IS NULL))), 0.0E0) AS [ProductPrice], COALESCE(SUM([o0].[Quantity]), 0) AS [TotalQuantitySold]
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
INNER JOIN [OrderItems] AS [o0] ON [o].[Id] = [o0].[OrderId]
INNER JOIN [ProductVariants] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductVariantId] = [p].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[ProductId]
    FROM [ProductImages] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] IN (
        SELECT [p0].[value]
        FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p0]
    ) AND [p].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    GROUP BY [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedBy], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[CreatedID], [t1].[DeleteBy], [t1].[DeleteId], [t1].[DeleteTime], [t1].[ImageFeature], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[IsThumbnail], [t1].[Path], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[UpdatedBy], [t1].[UpdatedDate], [t1].[UpdatedID]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreatedBy], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[CreatedID], [p1].[DeleteBy], [p1].[DeleteId], [p1].[DeleteTime], [p1].[ImageFeature], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[IsThumbnail], [p1].[Path], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[UpdatedBy], [p1].[UpdatedDate], [p1].[UpdatedID], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [p1].[ProductId] ORDER BY [p1].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [ProductImages] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ProductId] IN (
            SELECT [p2].[value]
            FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p2]
        ) AND [p1].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[ProductId] = [t0].[ProductId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[ProductId]
    FROM [ProductImages] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] IN (
        SELECT [p0].[value]
        FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p0]
    ) AND [p].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    GROUP BY [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedBy], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[CreatedID], [t1].[DeleteBy], [t1].[DeleteId], [t1].[DeleteTime], [t1].[ImageFeature], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[IsThumbnail], [t1].[Path], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[UpdatedBy], [t1].[UpdatedDate], [t1].[UpdatedID]

        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreatedBy], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[CreatedID], [p1].[DeleteBy], [p1].[DeleteId], [p1].[DeleteTime], [p1].[ImageFeature], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[IsThumbnail], [p1].[Path], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[UpdatedBy], [p1].[UpdatedDate], [p1].[UpdatedID], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [p1].[ProductId] ORDER BY [p1].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [ProductImages] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ProductId] IN (
            SELECT [p2].[value]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[ProductId]
    FROM [ProductImages] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] IN (
        SELECT [p0].[value]
        FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p0]
    ) AND [p].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    GROUP BY [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedBy], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[CreatedID], [t1].[DeleteBy], [t1].[DeleteId], [t1].[DeleteTime], [t1].[ImageFeature], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[IsThumbnail], [t1].[Path], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[UpdatedBy], [t1].[UpdatedDate], [t1].[UpdatedID]

        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreatedBy], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[CreatedID], [p1].[DeleteBy], [p1].[DeleteId], [p1].[DeleteTime], [p1].[ImageFeature], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[IsThumbnail], [p1].[Path], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[UpdatedBy], [p1].[UpdatedDate], [p1].[UpdatedID], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [p1].[ProductId] ORDER BY [p1].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [ProductImages] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ProductId] IN (
            SELECT [p2].[value]
            FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p2]
        ) AND [p1].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t1]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[ProductId] = [t0].[ProductId]

    SELECT [p].[ProductId]
    FROM [ProductImages] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] IN (
        SELECT [p0].[value]
        FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p0]
    ) AND [p].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    GROUP BY [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedBy], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[CreatedID], [t1].[DeleteBy], [t1].[DeleteId], [t1].[DeleteTime], [t1].[ImageFeature], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[IsThumbnail], [t1].[Path], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[UpdatedBy], [t1].[UpdatedDate], [t1].[UpdatedID]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreatedBy], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[CreatedID], [p1].[DeleteBy], [p1].[DeleteId], [p1].[DeleteTime], [p1].[ImageFeature], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[IsThumbnail], [p1].[Path], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[UpdatedBy], [p1].[UpdatedDate], [p1].[UpdatedID], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [p1].[ProductId] ORDER BY [p1].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [ProductImages] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ProductId] IN (
            SELECT [p2].[value]
            FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p2]
        ) AND [p1].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[ProductId] = [t0].[ProductId]
2024-07-01 01:13:00.569 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[@__productDTO_Id_0='?' (DbType = Guid)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

    FROM [ProductImages] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] IN (
        SELECT [p0].[value]
        FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p0]

) AS [t]

    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedBy], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[CreatedID], [t1].[DeleteBy], [t1].[DeleteId], [t1].[DeleteTime], [t1].[ImageFeature], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[IsThumbnail], [t1].[Path], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[UpdatedBy], [t1].[UpdatedDate], [t1].[UpdatedID]

            FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p2]
        ) AND [p1].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)

FROM [Products] AS [p]

        WHERE [p1].[ProductId] IN (
            SELECT [p2].[value]
            FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p2]
        ) AND [p1].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[ProductId] = [t0].[ProductId]

2024-07-01 01:13:36.683 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (5ms) [Parameters=[@__productIds_0='?' (Size = 4000)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedBy], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[CreatedID], [t0].[DeleteBy], [t0].[DeleteId], [t0].[DeleteTime], [t0].[ImageFeature], [t0].[IsDelete], [t0].[IsThumbnail], [t0].[Path], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[UpdatedBy], [t0].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[UpdatedID]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[ProductId]
    FROM [ProductImages] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] IN (
        SELECT [p0].[value]
        FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p0]
    ) AND [p].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    GROUP BY [p].[ProductId]
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedBy], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[CreatedID], [t1].[DeleteBy], [t1].[DeleteId], [t1].[DeleteTime], [t1].[ImageFeature], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[IsThumbnail], [t1].[Path], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[UpdatedBy], [t1].[UpdatedDate], [t1].[UpdatedID]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreatedBy], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[CreatedID], [p1].[DeleteBy], [p1].[DeleteId], [p1].[DeleteTime], [p1].[ImageFeature], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[IsThumbnail], [p1].[Path], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[UpdatedBy], [p1].[UpdatedDate], [p1].[UpdatedID], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [p1].[ProductId] ORDER BY [p1].[Id]) AS [row]
        FROM [ProductImages] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ProductId] IN (
            SELECT [p2].[value]
            FROM OPENJSON(@__productIds_0) WITH ([value] uniqueidentifier '$') AS [p2]
        ) AND [p1].[IsThumbnail] = CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t1]
    WHERE [t1].[row] <= 1
